3. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper discusses the use of millimeter wave frequencies in wireless systems, which can have implications for multimedia applications. 
4. cs.AR (Hardware Architecture): The paper discusses the physical layer design of wireless systems, which can have implications for hardware architecture. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the design of wireless systems, which can have implications for systems and control.
